data.description: Welcome to 1225 2nd St! Relax & unwind on the inviting covered front porch, perfect for savoring your morning coffee or indulging in a glass of wine. The beautiful kitchen features custom-built cabinetry, granite countertops, recessed lights, under cabinet lighting, new refrigerator & dishwasher. The dining room boasts built-ins that can be illuminated & new light fixture. Enjoy walking-out to the 3 car oversized garage from the newly built back entry. Upstairs offers owners suite w/custom floor to ceiling cabinetry w/mirror & included king-sized bed frame. Two additional bedrooms & updated full bath w/tiled floors & new tiled bath/shower completes this level. Lower level features plenty of space for storage & huge full bath. Stunning herringbone brick walkway. Located in a very desirable part of Beaver Borough. Close to a park & river. In walking distance to shopping, banking, library, post office & restaurants. Siding & roof 2011. Wiring & insulated Anderson windows 400 series 2007
